z=new O.l(["The bunks is a large, smelly, dark room with many bunk beds scattered around and not much else. Each bunk bed comes with tall personal lockers on each side. The only crewmember not housed here was the captain (and of course Gorilla, who has his den in the cargo bay).",new N.x4(this),[null,P.i(["goto","Bunks"])]],0,null,!1,!1)
