z=new O.l([new N.xj(this),new N.xk(this),new N.xl(this),"After a tiring and seemingly never-ending stretch of work, you look at the electronics and realize all the faulty components have been repaired or replaced. You link them together with new cables and turn the turret's power input back on, half-expecting another failure. But the turret just whirls to life, performing a quick self-test and switching on a green pilot light afterwards.","The turret is back online.",new N.xm(this),[null,P.i(["goto","Guts"])]],0,null,!1,!1)
