z=new O.l(["# Death","You leave the captain's cabin and head to the bridge, when suddenly you fall to your knees. At first, it's just like your legs temporarily gave out, but then comes the pain. Immense, excruciating pain, coming from the marrow to the skin. You fall on the side and open your mouth to scream, but only a squawk comes out.",[null,P.i(["string",new N.yV(),"goto","WaitIfItFades"]),P.i(["string",new N.yW(),"goto","CallGorilla"]),P.i(["string",new N.yX(),"goto","CrawlTowardsTheBridge"])],"- Crawl to the right (away from bridge, towards the engine room) // cures for a while"],0,null,!1,!1)
