z=new O.l(["This is the end.","You die.","..","..","..","Cold floor.","No other sensation.","Then, once again, you hear the blood humming in your veins.","The pain is back, too, but this time, it's not entirely unpleasant. It's like the pain is driving the death away, so you welcome it.",[null,P.i(["string",new N.yZ(),"goto","Ressurection: OpenEyes"])],"- TODO: something else, like Try to move, Get more rest"],0,null,!1,!1)
