z=new O.l(["Your jaw is still down in amazement when the Bodega starts talking through the PA. She doesn't bother to use the intercom anymore.",'"We just left the detection range of TODO and are on our way to TODO. In other words, you and your pet monkey are safe. You are welcome." ','Gorilla raises his browridge. "Actually, I am not a monkey. I am an ape. If I was a macaque, or similar, you could refer to me as a monkey. Am I a macaque, though? No. I am a gorilla." ',"At that moment, you realize: _this is how it's going to be here from now on._ TODO longer",'And the Bodega says: "Great, thanks for the lecture." And then, after a couple of seconds, she says with a different voice: "I suggest both of you apes come to the bridge. You might want to see this." '],0,null,!1,!1)
